{"lemma":"قَعْدَةٍ","slug":"قَعْدَةٍ","root":"ق.ع.د","root_slug":"ق-ع-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ع-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n35950","n35951","n35952","n35953","n35954"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%92%D8%AF%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n35950","headword_ar":"قَعْدَةٌ","root":"qEd","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A single sitting."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, Msb.) Ex."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaEada qaEodapF waAHidapF","text_ar":"قَعَدَ قَعْدَةً وَاحِدَةً"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sat a single sitting."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaEodapu rajulK","text_ar":"قَعْدَةُ رَجُلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiEodapN","text_ar":"قِعْدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in three places.       -A2-  And see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAEidN","text_ar":"قَاعِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw AlqaEodapi","text_ar":"ذُو القَعْدَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw","text_ar":"ذُو"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqiEodapi","text_ar":"القِعْدَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain month;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the eleventh month of the Arabian year;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"next after"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aw~aAl","text_ar":"شَوَّال"},{"kind":"text","text":": (L:) so called because the Arabs [when their year was solar] used to abstain ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaqoEuduwna","text_ar":"يَقْعُدُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":") therein from journeys (L, K, * TA) and warring and plundering expeditions and laying in stores of corn and seeking pasturage, before performing the pilgrimage in the next month; (L, TA;) or because in that month they broke in the young camels ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqiEodaAn","text_ar":"القِعْدَان"},{"kind":"text","text":") for riding: (Msb, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumaAdaY","text_ar":"جُمَادَى"},{"kind":"text","text":":) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*awaAtu AlqaEodapi","text_ar":"ذَوَاتُ القَعْدَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*awaAtu AlqaEadaAti","text_ar":"ذَوَاتُ القَعَدَاتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Yoo, Msb;) but the former is the regular pl., (Yoo,) because the two words are considered as one, (Msb,) and it is the more common: (TA:) dual"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*awaAtaA AlqaEodapi","text_ar":"ذَوَاتَا القَعْدَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*awaAtaA AlqaEodatayoni","text_ar":"ذَوَاتَا القَعْدَتَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["L","S","Msb","K","Yoo","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n35951","headword_ar":"قُعْدَةٌ","root":"qEd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quEadapN","text_ar":"قُعَدَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An ass:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quEodaAtN","text_ar":"قُعْدَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"E","text_ar":"ع"},{"kind":"text","text":"quiescent, (TA,) [in the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quEodaAnN","text_ar":"قُعْدَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quEadaAtN","text_ar":"قُعَدَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.)       -A2-  [The former,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A horse's,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a camel's saddle:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quEudaAtN","text_ar":"قُعُدَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IDrd, L,) with which is syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quEayodaAtN","text_ar":"قُعَيْدَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the dim.]. (S, L.) ―         -b2-  See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaEuwdN","text_ar":"قَعُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["K","L","TA","IDrd"]},{"entry_id":"n35952","headword_ar":"قِعْدَةٌ","root":"qEd","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner, of sitting."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, Msb, K.) Ex."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa Hasanu AlqiEodapi","text_ar":"هُوَ حَسَنُ القِعْدَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He has a good manner of sitting:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, L:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaEada qiEodapa Ald~ub~i","text_ar":"قَعَدَ قِعْدَةَ الدُّبِّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sat in the manner of sitting of the bear."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, * TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiEodapu rajulK","text_ar":"قِعْدَةُ رَجُلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulK","text_ar":"رَجُلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaEodapu","text_ar":"قَعْدَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, K, *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The space occupied by a man sitting:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the height,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"depth, of a man sitting."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) Ex."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ajarapN qiEodapu rajulK","text_ar":"شَجَرَةٌ قِعْدَةُ رَجُلٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A tree of the height of a man sitting:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, in L and TA, passim:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biy^orN qiEodapN","text_ar":"بِيْرٌ قِعْدَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A well of the depth of a man sitting:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eumoqu biy^orinaA qiEodapN","text_ar":"عُمْقُ بِيْرِنَا قِعْدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaEodapN","text_ar":"قَعْدَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The depth of our well is that of a man sitting:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) and"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2546},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA Hafarotu fiY AlA^aroDi A_il~aA qiEodapF","text_ar":"مَا حَفَرْتُ فِى الاَرْضِ اـِلَّا قِعْدَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaEodapF","text_ar":"قَعْدَةً","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I dug not in the ground save to the depth of a man sitting:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, L:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mararotu bimaA='K qiEodapi rajulK","text_ar":"مَرَرْتُ بِمَا=ءٍ قِعْدَةِ رَجُلٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I passed by water of the depth of a man sitting."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sb, L.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiEodapN","text_ar":"قِعْدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"One's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"last child, male or female;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one's last children."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["A","L","K","As","Lh"]},{"entry_id":"n35953","headword_ar":"قَعَدَةٌ","root":"qEd","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A vehicle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beast of carriage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"marokabN","text_ar":"مَرْكَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for women:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the copies of the K in our hands; (S, M;) but accord. to the L, &c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a man:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and it is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaEiydapN","text_ar":"قَعِيدَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"that bears the former signification. (TA.) ―         -b2-  The ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kind of carpet called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tanofasap","text_ar":"طَنْفَسَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] (L, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon which a man sits; and the like."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.)"}],"source_refs":["L","K"]},{"entry_id":"n35954","headword_ar":"قُعَدَةٌ","root":"qEd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quEodapN","text_ar":"قُعْدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quEodiY~N","text_ar":"قُعْدِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}